articles.title: Trump PAC foots bill for private investigator in Manhattan criminal case, E. Jean Carroll trial - CBS News
articles.description: A Trump PAC, Save America, paid more than $152,000 for a private eye's "research" in the former president's New York criminal and civil cases.
articles.content:
